<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>himepop</title>
  <meta name="description" content="himepop — a pastel personal link page" />
  <style>
    :root {
      --paper: #f8f4ea;
      --ink: #574739;
      --soft-ink: #746558;
      --pink: #efc7d9;
      --blue: #b9d7ee;
      --green: #9fdc9c;
      --yellow: #f4d868;
      --peach: #e9b17a;
      --sand: #c7b18c;
      --line: #7c6c5b;
      --white: #fffdf8;
      --shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(87, 71, 57, 0.12);
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
      color: var(--ink);
      background: var(--paper);
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.3), rgba(255,255,255,0.3)),
        radial-gradient(circle at 20% 10%, rgba(239,199,217,.35), transparent 25%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 80% 20%, rgba(185,215,238,.35), transparent 26%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 20% 80%, rgba(159,220,156,.25), transparent 22%);
      padding: 28px;
    }

    .site {
      max-width: 1050px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      border: 2.5px solid var(--line);
      background: rgba(255,253,248,0.9);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .masthead {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 1fr;
      border-bottom: 2.5px solid var(--line);
    }

    .title-panel,
    .intro-panel,
    .grid-card,
    .bio-card,
    .footer-card {
      min-width: 0;
    }

    .title-panel {
      padding: 26px 28px 20px;
      border-right: 2.5px solid var(--line);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(244,216,104,.18), rgba(239,199,217,.12));
    }

    .eyebrow {
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      color: var(--soft-ink);
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: clamp(3rem, 9vw, 7rem);
      line-height: 0.9;
      letter-spacing: -0.05em;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .bubble {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 14px;
      padding: 10px 16px;
      border: 2px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--white);
      font-size: 1rem;
      transform: rotate(-2deg);
    }

    .intro-panel {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-rows: auto 1fr;
      background: var(--blue);
    }

    .intro-top {
      padding: 18px 20px;
      border-bottom: 2.5px solid var(--line);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.24);
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.55;
    }

    .shapes {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 0;
      min-height: 260px;
    }

    .shape {
      border-right: 2.5px solid var(--line);
      border-bottom: 2.5px solid var(--line);
      min-height: 130px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .shape:nth-child(1) { background: var(--green); }
    .shape:nth-child(2) { background: #f6efcf; }
    .shape:nth-child(3) { background: var(--pink); border-right: 0; }
    .shape:nth-child(4) { background: var(--peach); border-bottom: 0; }
    .shape:nth-child(5) { background: var(--white); border-bottom: 0; }
    .shape:nth-child(6) { background: #d6c0a0; border-right: 0; border-bottom: 0; }

    .wavy::before,
    .wavy::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      left: 12%;
      right: 12%;
      height: 14px;
      border: 2px solid var(--line);
      border-left: 0;
      border-right: 0;
      border-radius: 999px;
    }

    .wavy::before { top: 36px; }
    .wavy::after { top: 76px; }

    .rings::before,
    .rings::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      border: 2px solid rgba(87,71,57,.45);
      border-radius: 50%;
    }

    .rings::before {
      width: 180px;
      height: 180px;
      right: -36px;
      bottom: -34px;
    }

    .rings::after {
      width: 120px;
      height: 120px;
      right: -6px;
      bottom: -6px;
    }

    .flower::before,
    .flower::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      margin: auto;
      width: 62px;
      height: 62px;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 50% 15%, #f8d1df 0 20%, transparent 21%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 85% 50%, #f8d1df 0 20%, transparent 21%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 50% 85%, #f8d1df 0 20%, transparent 21%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 15% 50%, #f8d1df 0 20%, transparent 21%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, var(--yellow) 0 16%, transparent 17%);
    }

    .spark::before {
      content: "✦";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      font-size: 48px;
      color: var(--yellow);
    }

    .main-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.1fr .9fr;
    }

    .left-column {
      border-right: 2.5px solid var(--line);
      display: grid;
      grid-template-rows: auto auto;
    }

    .bio-card {
      padding: 28px;
      border-bottom: 2.5px solid var(--line);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,.55), rgba(239,199,217,.15));
    }

    .bio-card h2,
    .links-card h2,
    .mini-card h3 {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }

    .bio-card p,
    .links-card p,
    .mini-card p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: var(--soft-ink);
    }

    .links-card {
      padding: 0;
      background: var(--white);
    }

    .links-head {
      padding: 18px 22px;
      border-bottom: 2.5px solid var(--line);
      background: rgba(185,215,238,.25);
    }

    .links-list {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }

    .link-box {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--ink);
      padding: 24px 22px;
      min-height: 126px;
      border-right: 2.5px solid var(--line);
      border-bottom: 2.5px solid var(--line);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
      transition: background .15s ease, transform .15s ease;
    }

    .link-box:nth-child(1) { background: rgba(239,199,217,.55); }
    .link-box:nth-child(2) { background: rgba(159,220,156,.4); border-right: 0; }
    .link-box:nth-child(3) { background: rgba(244,216,104,.35); border-bottom: 0; }
    .link-box:nth-child(4) { background: rgba(185,215,238,.45); border-right: 0; border-bottom: 0; }

    .link-box:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.75);
    }

    .link-name {
      font-size: 1.35rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .link-url {
      font-size: .95rem;
      color: var(--soft-ink);
      word-break: break-word;
    }

    .right-column {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-rows: 1.1fr .9fr;
    }

    .hero-card {
      position: relative;
      min-height: 420px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(239,199,217,.8), rgba(239,199,217,.5));
      border-bottom: 2.5px solid var(--line);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero-card::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      width: 230px;
      height: 230px;
      border-radius: 46% 54% 63% 37% / 50% 35% 65% 50%;
      background: var(--sand);
      left: 32px;
      top: 110px;
      transform: rotate(-18deg);
      opacity: .85;
    }

    .hero-card::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      width: 210px;
      height: 110px;
      right: 28px;
      bottom: 34px;
      background: var(--blue);
      border-radius: 60% 40% 60% 40% / 60% 50% 50% 40%;
      border: 2.5px solid var(--line);
    }

    .drop {
      position: absolute;
      left: 88px;
      bottom: 94px;
      width: 120px;
      height: 160px;
      background: #ffd6e6;
      border: 2.5px solid var(--line);
      clip-path: path('M60 0 C90 42 120 82 120 112 C120 145 93 160 60 160 C27 160 0 145 0 112 C0 82 30 42 60 0 Z');
      transform: rotate(8deg);
    }

    .tag {
      position: absolute;
      top: 24px;
      right: 24px;
      background: var(--white);
      border: 2px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 10px 16px;
      font-size: 15px;
      transform: rotate(-4deg);
    }

    .caption {
      position: absolute;
      left: 26px;
      bottom: 24px;
      right: 26px;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: var(--soft-ink);
      background: rgba(255,253,248,.76);
      border: 2px solid rgba(124,108,91,.7);
      padding: 12px 14px;
    }

    .mini-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }

    .mini-card {
      padding: 20px;
      min-height: 160px;
      border-right: 2.5px solid var(--line);
    }

    .mini-card:last-child { border-right: 0; }
    .mini-card:nth-child(1) { background: rgba(244,216,104,.18); }
    .mini-card:nth-child(2) { background: rgba(159,220,156,.18); }

    .mini-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 14px;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border: 2px solid var(--line);
      background: var(--white);
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .footer-card {
      border-top: 2.5px solid var(--line);
      padding: 14px 20px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 18px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--soft-ink);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.55);
    }

    @media (max-width: 860px) {
      .masthead,
      .main-grid,
      .links-list,
      .mini-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .title-panel,
      .left-column,
      .mini-card,
      .link-box {
        border-right: 0;
      }

      .left-column { border-right: 0; }
      .link-box:nth-child(1),
      .link-box:nth-child(3) { border-right: 0; }
      .link-box:nth-child(3) { border-bottom: 2.5px solid var(--line); }
      .mini-card:first-child { border-bottom: 2.5px solid var(--line); }
      .footer-card { flex-direction: column; }
      .hero-card { min-height: 360px; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 580px) {
      body { padding: 14px; }
      .title-panel, .bio-card, .links-head, .mini-card, .intro-top, .caption { padding-left: 16px; padding-right: 16px; }
      h1 { font-size: 3.2rem; }
      .shapes { min-height: 210px; }
      .shape { min-height: 105px; }
      .hero-card::before { width: 170px; height: 170px; left: 18px; top: 118px; }
      .drop { left: 44px; width: 96px; height: 132px; }
      .hero-card::after { width: 150px; height: 80px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="site">
    <section class="masthead">
      <div class="title-panel">
        <div class="eyebrow">personal site / link archive</div>
        <h1>himepop</h1>
        <div class="bubble">welcome ♡</div>
      </div>

      <div class="intro-panel">
        <div class="intro-top">
          A soft little corner for stories, films, code, and thoughts. Built like a tiny poster board — bright, tidy, and easy to click through.
        </div>
        <div class="shapes">
          <div class="shape flower"></div>
          <div class="shape wavy"></div>
          <div class="shape rings"></div>
          <div class="shape"></div>
          <div class="shape spark"></div>
          <div class="shape"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="main-grid">
      <div class="left-column">
        <section class="bio-card">
          <h2>about</h2>
          <p>I keep this page for the things I love returning to: late-night coding, favorite fics, beautiful films, and small internet corners that still feel personal.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="links-card">
          <div class="links-head">
            <h2>links</h2>
            <p>Tap any box to visit the real page.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="links-list">
            <a class="link-box" href="https://github.com/yourusername" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
              <span class="link-name">GitHub</span>
              <span class="link-url">github.com/yourusername</span>
            </a>
            <a class="link-box" href="https://archiveofourown.org/users/yourusername" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
              <span class="link-name">AO3</span>
              <span class="link-url">archiveofourown.org/users/yourusername</span>
            </a>
            <a class="link-box" href="https://x.com/yourusername" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
              <span class="link-name">X</span>
              <span class="link-url">x.com/yourusername</span>
            </a>
            <a class="link-box" href="https://letterboxd.com/yourusername/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
              <span class="link-name">Letterboxd</span>
              <span class="link-url">letterboxd.com/yourusername</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>

      <div class="right-column">
        <section class="hero-card">
          <div class="tag">pastel web home</div>
          <div class="drop"></div>
          <div class="caption">
            Inspired by editorial pastel layouts: playful blocks, hand-drawn warmth, and a homepage that feels more like a printed spread than a plain link list.
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mini-grid">
          <div class="mini-card">
            <h3>note</h3>
            <p>Replace each <em>yourusername</em> with your real handle before uploading.</p>
            <div class="mini-badge">index.html ready</div>
          </div>
          <div class="mini-card">
            <h3>style</h3>
            <p>Soft paper tones, graphic panels, and simple shapes keep it cute without feeling cluttered.</p>
            <div class="mini-badge">himepop online</div>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="footer-card">
      <span>himepop — personal links and favorites</span>
      <span>GitHub Pages friendly / single-file HTML</span>
    </footer>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
